modName: Vlad from Dracula Untold - Luke Evans preset
summary: Luke Evans preset for a handsome vampsome
descriptionHtml:
Did you watch Dracula Untold and think, "wow, he Luke Evans is the perfect Dracula what a badass dude"? yeah? well boy howdy do I have the RaceMenu Preset for you!

Installation
1. Download and open the WinRar folder
2. Find your presets folder, my path isÂ C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\Chargen\Presets
3. place the "Vlad the Impaler.jslot" file in your presets folder
4. Play skyrim and press F9 in the presets section while in racemenu
